snippet.title: Bunhouse Trailer
snippet.description:
The Kickstarter is Live!
Kickstarter link: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/patrickgauthier/bunhouse-be-a-bun-grow-some-plants-play-with-friends

Hey cool cats. I know most people follow me for my few Hamilton r/WSB parodies I have put out, but I also happen to be a video game developer! I am currently preparing to launch a Kickstarter for my upcoming game, Bunhouse.

Bunhouse is a cute couch co-op greenhouse management game where you play as a bunny. The Kickstarter launches on May 13th, 2021 at 12pm EST. You can check out the Kickstarter page at the link above.

If you would enjoy this game or know anyone who would, I would be so grateful if you would share this page, this video, or anything else to help me spread the leafy love.


Kickstarter link: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/patrickgauthier/bunhouse-be-a-bun-grow-some-plants-play-with-friends
Steam link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1617430/Bunhouse/
Discord link: https://discord.gg/r6PK3Cv
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RekyStudios
